4
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:05.300
Don't you believe it?

5
00:00:05.300 --> 00:00:06.233
You go to the frontier

6
00:00:06.266 --> 00:00:08.000
Find your father's body

7
00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:09.600
See if it's a one-shot kill.

8
00:00:09.600 --> 00:00:10.666
You are lying

9
00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:12.466
My father is invincible

10
00:00:12.466 --> 00:00:15.900
Dongying Fang's world strength is also in the top five

11
00:00:16.100 --> 00:00:17.833
How could it be killed with one move?

12
00:00:18.200 --> 00:00:19.966
You're a bit of a stalker

13
00:00:19.966 --> 00:00:21.533
We tell you the truth

14
00:00:21.533 --> 00:00:22.400
If you don't believe

15
00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.566
You look for clues on your father's body

16
00:00:25.100 --> 00:00:26.633
What's the use of us, Xiaojin?

17
00:00:26.666 --> 00:00:29.033
Don't tell their cunning Great Xia Zhu so much

18
00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:31.200
Just kill them and reinvestigate

19
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:32.200
Kill the wrong one

20
00:00:32.200 --> 00:00:33.633
I don't know about you two.

21
00:00:33.666 --> 00:00:35.333
Did you watch the afternoon news?

22
00:00:35.333 --> 00:00:36.200
