23
00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:38.500
There are two important messages in the news:

24
00:00:38.500 --> 00:00:39.600
At the entry ceremony

25
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:41.366
Your Gao Xuanyun was just wronged.

26
00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:43.933
But I didn't say you are the woman of Long Ru 2

27
00:00:43.933 --> 00:00:46.266
This Liao Fan is Long Shuai's substitute samurai

28
00:00:46.266 --> 00:00:47.866
Not some irrelevant person

29
00:00:50.133 --> 00:00:51.500
Yeah, but what does that mean?

30
00:00:51.500 --> 00:00:53.200
I am indeed Long Shuai's wife

31
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.766
But he died before he could give me my name.

32
00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.666
Nonsense is still here

33
00:00:58.866 --> 00:01:00.533
Anyway, Ouyang Mu has already said

34
00:01:00.533 --> 00:01:03.300
Shen Liao Fan is the murderer who ambushed the god of ninjas

35
00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:04.766
Kill him once and for all

36
00:01:04.766 --> 00:01:07.166
Sure enough, Ouyang Tomb sent you here.

37
00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:09.066
The imperial teacher told him not to disclose his identity

38
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:10.400
How dare you violate my arrangement?

39
00:01:10.400 --> 00:01:12.000
Anyway, his mother is going to be dead soon

40
00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:13.466
Why pay so much attention?

